{"tid":229061,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[手作jj]手工藝，文具討論","createTime":"2017-05-04T10:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T16:45:46.000Z","uid":62573,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"842191292eb9a311d64c4cdc71059fc683744f89","tid":229061,"uid":62573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"唔知連登多唔多人中意DIY<br />\n皮革手繩甚至銀飾都見過有post<br />\n喺呢度希望召集一班玩開DIY MT 拼貼卡片 嘅同好一齊討論下分享大家嘅作品<br />\n無類係咩類形都好都互相交流下<br />\n始終小妹玩嘅都好廣範<br />\n想有更多人認識同接觸手作制品<br />\n<br />\n入黎嘅您，留低你嘅作品同心得甚至係教學一齊欣賞交流下<br />\n<br />\n先貼為敬，勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/733f24X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F733f24X.jpg&h=63d8486a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1e5ZHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1e5ZHQ.jpg&h=0aca7c74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/185138_3fa049a1f496ef35813d6385f66b1b5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F185138_3fa049a1f496ef35813d6385f66b1b5d.jpg&h=b22c79d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Cd6P93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Cd6P93.jpg&h=16396148&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1de1e012571fd2cdfa7b67af0793fb12818c7ea","tid":229061,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"文具控來留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03233236551ce820bdbea9d4b21b7f9ea4499101","tid":229061,"uid":62573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文具控來留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好中意睇文具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/lov